description: Photographer Lucas Leon, is about to get one of his biggest breaks by shooting rising football star Deangelo Jackson. When they start the shoot Lucas is very nervous and Deangelo can sense it. He puts him in various poses and takes some beautiful photographs. Deangelo starts getting very horny while taking these pictures and Lucas is not bad to look at either. When the two men’s eyes lock, it’s on and they’re exploring each other‘s cocks and assholes. Deangelo fucks him right there against his grand piano.
title: Shooting The Pro
